### Sources of Air pollution

Many of the pollutants in our atmosphere have `natural as well as human-related origins`. The two major kinds of air pollution sources are:
1. **Stationary sources**
2. **Mobile sources**
:::

:::.col-12 .col-md-6
![img](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Nh-emon/QDoc/main/SES3/Soil%20and%20Enviromental%20Quality/resources/air-quality-dgrm2.png)
:::
:::
